<p>The case has a simple design but it still looks great - available in both black and white, the NZXT H500i has a nice side panel window and a bunch of cool features.</p>

<p>For starters, it comes with an Adaptive Noise Reduction Algorithm that changes fan speed automatically based on temperatures.</p>

<p>This way, your case fans will only run as hard as they need to, thus reducing noise and increasing efficiency.</p>

<p>The H500i comes with all of the fancy bells and whistles you‚Äôd expect from a high end case but for a modest price.</p>

<p>With this model, the H500i has a smart hub for fan control and a built-in RGB strip up top and behind a cable cover.</p>

<p>This case has a sleek white paint job that‚Äôs minimalistic but super good looking.</p>

<p>It also features a nice side panel window that allows you to display your components, illuminated by the case‚Äôs RGB lighting.</p>

