<p>Unlike a lot of other cases on the market, this one has a unique design that makes it stand out from the crowd.</p>

<p>That unique feature is, of course, the dual-chamber design.</p>

<p>Components that don‚Äôt need direct cooling (PSU, hard drives) are stored in the bottom chamber, and the motherboard goes in the chamber on top where most of the airflow is.</p>

<p>This makes it so no airflow is wasted ‚Äì the components that need to be constantly cooled get maximum exposure to your case fans, and the components that aren‚Äôt as important stay tucked out of the way.</p>

<p>As an added bonus, in case you‚Äôre always on the go, this case also has nice carrying handles that make transportation easy.</p>

<p>That being said, if you‚Äôre the kind of gamer that likes to have LAN parties, this is the casse for you.</p>

